A sweepline algorithm for Voronoi diagrams.
Algorithmica, 2(2), 1987, 153-174.

 Watson D. F.
Computing n-dimensional Delaunay tesselation with
application to Voronoi polytopes.
Computer Jour., V.24, #2, 167-172.

